About This Company
Tangent has over 30 years experience in the telecommunications and IT industry.
We have a wealth of knowledge in the international recruitment market, having placed telecommunication and IT staff in over 97 countries across the globe. Tangent is also committed to the development, implementation and on-going improvement of Quality Management (QM) in conformance with the globally recognised quality standard, British Standard BS EN ISO 9001.2000.
Some of our facts:
25 years experience of the Middle East and Africa
Over 30 years experience in providing Global Recruitment Solutions
Global Database of 120 Nationalities
Provided IT & Telecom expertise into 97 countries
Tangent is British standard BS EN ISO 9001/2000 quality accredited
